    • Method Detail

      • SetCells

        private void SetCells()
        SetCells - purpose of this method is to create a HashMap of all the cells in the puzzle. If the puzzle is 9X9, there will be 81 cells in the puzzle. The key for the HashMap is the Cell's hash code The value for the HashMap is the Cell. The values in the HashSet for each cell's valid values should be shuffled
        Since:
        Lab #4
